flowRoot.flowPara: Bring the whole whānau for a day of making and creating with technology! We have joined forces with Mozilla to participate in their global Maker Party campaign celebrating making and web literacy.
There will be heaps to do:
We can't wait to see what you will create!
• Create your own video games with MakerBox
• See digital 3D modelling and printing in action with Wellington MMakerspace
• Express yourself with open source multimedia at the Fedora booth
• See what local students are creating at Raroa Normal Intermediate's Mdiscovery station
• Make mobile media, stream and publish from your smartphone with MMohawk Media
We can't wait to see what you create!
